          <p><a href="https://forum.moparisthebest.com/u/fedexer">@fedexer</a> wrote:</p>
          <blockquote>
              <p>sure mate , add <code>if (npcs[i].npcType == NPCID) { //  (at NPCID at the santa's id
						if (misc.random2(30) == 1) {
							npcs[i].updateRequired = true;
							npcs[i].textUpdateRequired = true;
							npcs[i].textUpdate = "Ho Ho HO Merry  christmas";
						}</code></p>
<p>you add this in your npchandler.java</p>
<p>search for “moo” and add this code under it  <img src="https://forum.moparisthebest.com/images/emoji/twitter/wink.png?v=6" title=":wink:" class="emoji" alt=":wink:">  hope that helps… also i would post in runescape development section next time… as this is the wrong section</p>
